#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a user manual stub for &kgeotag;, the stand-alone photo geotagging "
"program. At the moment, there's not much to see here apart from the general "
"information you can find on <ulink url=\"https://kgeotag.kde.org/"
"\">KGeoTag's homepage</ulink>, but hopefully, this will change in the "
"future ;-)"
msgstr ""
"To je uporabniški priročnik za &kgeotag;, samostojni program za geografsko "
"označevanje fotografij. Trenutno tukaj ni veliko videti, razen splošnih "
"informacij, ki jih lahko najdete na <ulink url=\"https://kgeotag.kde.org/"
"\">domači strani KGeoTag</ulink>, vendar upajmo, da se bo to spremenilo "
"prihodnosti ;-)"

